{"tid":1855934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平痛斥有外國人「吃飽了沒事幹」指中國不去折騰外國","createTime":"2020-02-01T10:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T00:30:06.000Z","uid":103981,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4957f0616181d3762bda04760bb4b14bb51d577e","tid":1855934,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"中共的國家副主席習近平11日在墨西哥與當地華僑見面時表示：在國際金融風暴中，中國能夠基本解決13億人口的吃飯問題，已經是對全人類最偉大的貢獻。他還指出，有少數外國人對中國事務說三道四：「有些吃飽了沒事幹的外國人，對我們的事情指手畫腳。中國一不輸出革命，二不輸出飢餓和貧困，三不去折騰你們，還有什麼好說的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2009-02-16/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%8D%E3%80%8D%E5%91%8A%E8%A8%B4%E4%B8%96%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-74641520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2009-02-16%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%259A%2584%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25B8%258D%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E4%25B8%2596%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC-74641520&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5ItTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=6bc918c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2009-02-16/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%8D%E3%80%8D%E5%91%8A%E8%A8%B4%E4%B8%96%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-74641520</a>"},{"pid":"3f42311ea2fa2ab58b0dc3717d35ca8aa8459196","tid":1855934,"uid":103981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8895fdcd6c37ef9b82b9bcab4ae24cb19f73e2f6","tid":1855934,"uid":41545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"BINC?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb001efadd9151efa527df7cc0c8abacc6f95dd","tid":1855934,"uid":144541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10